          "range": "4790-4884",
          "rangeStart": 4790,
          "rangeEnd": 4884,
          "markText": "远期合约(forward contract)，是远期合约交易的简称，是一种相对简单的金融衍生工具，是指交易双方达成的在未来某一日期（远期）按照约定价格进行某种资产交易的协议。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1765078611,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-12-07 11:36:51",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119939&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4790&rangeEnd=4884",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c9332fa0813ab9559g01990b?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4790&rangeEnd=4884"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "第二篇 金融市场篇",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119939_10_6347-6385",
          "range": "6347-6385",
          "rangeStart": 6347,
          "rangeEnd": 6385,
          "markText": "融通资金功能，即实现储蓄向投资转化的功能，这是金融市场最主要、最基本的功能。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1765078608,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-12-07 11:36:48",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119939&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6347&rangeEnd=6385",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c9332fa0813ab9559g01990b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6347&rangeEnd=6385"
        }
      ]
    }
